GSD.description:
ethernet: aeroflex: fix potential skb leak in greth_init_rings()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.159 by commit 87277bdf2c370ab2d07cfe77dfa9b37f82bbe1e5, it was introduced in version v2.6.34 by commit d4c41139df6e74c6fff0cbac43e51cab782133be. For more details please see the references link.
